answers.text: estimated in 2001 to support around 23,000 people

qas.question: Một số điểm tham quan của quận là

answers.text: the coastal towns, part of the Exmoor National Park, the West Somerset Railway (a heritage railway), and the museum of the Fleet Air Arm at RNAS Yeovilton

qas.question: Glastonbury có các mối liên kết với

answers.text: mythical associations, including legends of a visit by the young Jesus of Nazareth and Joseph of Arimathea, with links to the Holy Grail, King Arthur

qas.question: Lễ hội Glastonbury nổi tiếng như thế nào

answers.text: Glastonbury also gives its name to an annual open-air rock festival held in nearby Pilton

qas.question: Loại phô mai nào là loại hạt nổi tiếng

answers.text: locally produced cheese, although there is now only one remaining cheese maker in the village of Cheddar
